high_descs: Turn around and get to the desk with the TV on it.
Pick up the cardboard box.
Turn back around and turn left to face the table.
Place the box on top of the table.
Turn right then go right again.
Pick up the box that's in the chair.
Turn right and go back to the table.
Place the box on the table behind the statue.
anns.task_desc: Place 2 cardboard boxes on the table.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the cabinet the TV is on.
Pick up the box to the left of the TV.
Turn around and go stand between the coffee table and the couch, facing the coffee table.
Place the box between the lap top and the statue.
Turn around and go to the chair to the left of the couch.
Pick up the box on the chair.
Go back to the coffee table.
Place the box behind the statue.
anns.task_desc: Put two boxes on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn right and begin walking to the pink chair, then hang a right and walk around the coffee table to the large dresser with the television on it.
Pick up the cardboard box on the dresser to the left of the television.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn left and walk up to the side of the coffee table that the couch is on.
Place the cardboard box on the coffee table in between the statue and laptop.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the pink chair.
Pick up the cardboard box off of the seat of the chair.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, stop at the middle of the coffee table and turn right, then walk forward.
Place the cardboard box on the coffee table behind the statue.
anns.task_desc: Move two cardboard boxes to a coffee table.
